First, the requisite caveats: Blazy has not told me that he is the next cre=
ative director of Chanel. In fact, he has said
nothing when people have asked him directly. Leena Nair, the C.E.O. of Chan=
el, has not confirmed anything to me, either, and the Wertheimer brothers, =
who own Chanel, haven=E2=80=99t talked to a journalist in 20 years. (And ev=
en then, it wasn=E2=80=99t about Chanel=E2=80=A6) Also, deals fall through,=
